    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>A Goblin Runner is a small, fast skirmisher driven from deep mountain caves by an unknown force pressing southwest. It moves with frantic energy, lives by speed, and dies cheap.</p>",
      "director": "<p>Runners exist to swarm and exploit the Monarch's orders. Crafty means they never provoke opportunity attacks, so they charge freely through packed lines. Use them to tie up ranged attackers or pile onto isolated targets. Kill the Monarch first or the Runners become a death of a thousand paper cuts.</p>",
